casebody.data:
Jose Contreras MORALES, BY AND THROUGH his Guardian ad litem, Liliana Morales FERNANDEZ, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
SUSSEX COUNTY COMMUNITY COLLEGE and Sophie Dutkowski, Defendants-Respondents,
and
Carroll Services, Inc., Defendant,
and
Fidel Rodriguez and Campbell's Small Engine Sales and Service, Inc., Defendants. C-433 September Term 2017
080107 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 13, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000305-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
